data.title: The Smiling Lieutenant
data.text:
1931, 93 min. Directed by Ernst Lubitsch. Starring Maurice Chevalier, Claudette Colbert and Miriam Hopkins.

Essential Cinema: Pre-Code Treasures: A sexy pre-Hollywood censorship musical about a man who marries a princess and takes his girlfriend along for the ride.

6406 N. I-35 Ste. 3100, 512/322-0145
